React: After this rogue targets a character with a melee strike: The rogue may not perform any other Reacts during this strike. Select one of the following:
the strike inflicts an additional wound if it hits;
add +8 to the die roll;
discard an item equipped by the target after the strike hits (before wounds are inflicted).

React: Before Cordeos Reborn kills target opposing character: Summon 1 character into your front rank, based on the target's Level.
Level 1-2: Mummy;
Level 3-4: Karem Tansiq;
Level 5+: Poison Avatar.

After Caedmon enters play, roll a die and apply the following bonuses to Caedmon permanently:
1-5, +3 AC and +1 Hit Point;
6-10, +6 ATK and +4 AC;
11-15, +5 ATK, AC and skill;
16-20, two additional strikes (Base +5).
